These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, boat, ship
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, rat
House: craftsman, art-deco, futuristic
 1. the craftsman house is the owner of the pony##1
 2. the futuristic house is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the rat and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the designer is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person driving the ship is the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the art-deco house is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Transport         | boat    | ship  | bus        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Pet   | pony     | rabbit  | rat       |
| House         | craftsman     | art-deco | futuristic |

