.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
House: futuristic, palace, farmhouse
City: venice, rome, liverpool
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff, tiparillo
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the pony is the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the farmhouse house##1
 3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the futuristic house##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| House   | futuristic  | farmhouse  | palace     |
| City   | liverpool       | rome      | venice         |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | davidoff   | game    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

