.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, milk
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, tulip
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the russian is the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who growsrose is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person playing snooker is between the indian and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the indian is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage          | milk      | hot-chocolate      | water      |
| Game         | backgammon   | snooker | scrabble |
| Flower   | dahlia | rose    | tulip          |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | folk      | r&b          |
| Nationality   | indian    | egyptian  | russian      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Sport         | climbing  | sailing   | swimming     |

