 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the colonial house and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | colonial | gothic-revival      | ranch-style      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| City   | london  | marseilles     | san-francisco |
| Cigar           | bongani        | aristoff | swisher     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

