.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dunhill, blend
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
3 different games are played: domino, billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, metal, blues
1. the chaman-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the fan of blues is the person playing domino##1
3. the dressmaker is between the blend-smoker and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the fan of blues##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the fisherman is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the fan of pop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | dunhill    | chaman       | blend      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Game         | billiard | domino   | monopoly  |
| Music-Genre     | metal    | blues     | pop      |

 